{"tid":132154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林健鋒擬兩會提出支港兩地聯合推動國民教育阻港獨入侵","createTime":"2017-02-23T15:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T14:32:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07fef3818cca1fbed67d35f934962b9613046141","tid":132154,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1315328-20170223.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1315328-20170223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=618d797d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1315328-20170223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=27a939ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1315328-20170223.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n全支兩會將於下月在北京舉行，政協委員林健鋒將會提出支港兩地聯手推動國民教育，阻止「港獨」入侵中小學的提案。<br />\n<br />\n林健鋒建議，安排支那知名專家與本地教育界合作，共同編寫、修訂適合香港採用的權威教材，確立學生的國家憲制概念和國民身份意識。他又提出，兩地學術機構聯手為教師提供反「港獨」教學支援，加強本港反「港獨」教育。<br />\n<br />\n另外，4名經民聯的政協委員提出聯名提案，建議開放擁有電子護照的支那居民可在網上籤註赴港「自由行」。"},{"pid":"c3e138fe8dd13d91d82121c16c782b4567b8171a","tid":132154,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f231d52f9a1e8f0da67fb18c8379f7090e7bec9b","tid":132154,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:24:28.000Z","msg":"賣港賊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a93f7e689b4edd7ef2147813daf4b8c54709f3","tid":132154,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:32:30.000Z","msg":"唔好，中港台三地一齊推動國民教育最好"}]}